Download jadx.zip 
Unzip jadz.zip

sudo mv jadx /opt/jadx

(Professional Setup) run from any path

1️⃣ Make the real executables runnable
sudo chmod +x /opt/jadx/bin/jadx
sudo chmod +x /opt/jadx/bin/jadx-gui

2️⃣ Create global commands (run from anywhere)
sudo ln -s /opt/jadx/bin/jadx /usr/local/bin/jadx
sudo ln -s /opt/jadx/bin/jadx-gui /usr/local/bin/jadx-gui
